summary: This episode was so wholesome and so cool at the same time!! Peter’s relationship with Miles has been so sweet to see because...
body: This episode was so wholesome and so cool at the same time!! Peter’s relationship with Miles has been so sweet to see because it’s been cool to watch him become a mentor to him as both Peter and Spider Man. It makes me wonder if Miles is going to learn of Peter’s secret identity or not which will be very interesting to see. Not to mention the boss fight with Martin inside Pete’s mind was very cool and the last scene with Peter and MJ was so sweet as well! Definitely looking forward to more of this game!!

summary: Reasons why I am not ready for the next avengers movie and why I’ll never be.
body:
Reasons why I am not ready for the next avengers movie and why I’ll never be.

When Thanos snapped his ugly ass eggplant looking fingers half of the life on earth died, what if May died, what is Ned died? And fucking MJ, she’s a fucking queen, what if she died? What happend to Mr. Delmar, WHAT HAPPEND TO HIS CAT!? Imagine all kids who became orphans.


This whole post is a mess but I just can’t stop thinking about it, and what if May survived, she lost the only family she had, like it was always her and Peter and then he dies as well.

I’m gonna stop now or I’ll start crying again
